OL,12,Fhe was ruled ineligible by the Unite
OL,13,Funion due to "a new rule that no one
OL,14,Fwas aware of" which meant only one
OL,15,Fcandidate - Vaughan Gething - was put
OL,16,Fforward for nomination.
