OL,3,CLeadership contender claims he was
OL,4,Cunfairly blocked from union nomination
OL,6,FIn a statement Jeremy Miles said that
OL,7,Fwas when he was told "for the first
OL,8,Ftime that I was ineligible to be
OL,9,Fnominated by the union due to a new
OL,10,Frule that no one was aware of, had not
OL,11,Fbeen published and which hadn't been
OL,12,Fapplied previously. The political
OL,13,Fcommittee was then prevented from
OL,14,Fvoting to express a view on the
OL,15,Fcandidates, in light of this new rule.
