OL,3,CLeadership contender claims he was
OL,4,Cunfairly blocked from union nomination
OL,6,F"This new rule was not declared when I
OL,7,Fwas invited by Unite to attend and
OL,8,Fparticipate in the nomination
OL,9,Fhustings. Neither was it referred to
OL,10,Fduring the hustings. After the
OL,11,Fhustings concluded, the leadership of
OL,12,FUnite failed to mention it to me. To
OL,13,Fdate, I have not seen any evidence the
OL,14,Frule even exists for the purpose
OL,15,Fclaimed.
OL,17,F"Members will rightly expect that
OL,18,Frules to nominate a candidate for the
OL,19,Fnext leader of our party and our
OL,20,Fgovernment should be transparent and
OL,21,Fbe applied fairly.
